              Exceptional experience working the Sandy.  Her attention to detail is unsurpassed. Sandy is super easy to work with.  
              Her communication is great.  We worked very closely on my project... 
              <br><br><span style="font-family:MontserratRegular">Joye H</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="slide">
          <div>
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            <a href="/reviews#Rupprecht" class="review-text" style="text-decoration: none;">
